<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lv">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Rēķins {{ invoice_number }}</title>
    <style>
        @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        html, body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 9px;
            line-height: 1.25;
            color: #000;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .page {
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            padding: 11mm 12mm 14mm 12mm;
            position: relative;
        }
        .hdr-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; }
        .meta { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
        .meta-block .lbl { color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); font-size: 7px; }
        .meta-block .val { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 2px; }
        .logo-block { text-align: right; font-size: 6px; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); max-width: 120px; }
        .logo-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: #000; }
        hr.line { border: none; border-top: 0.5px solid #ccc; margin: 8px 0; }
        .two-col { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-top: 6px; }
        .col { width: 50%; }
        .sec-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 9px; margin-bottom: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; }
        .dot { width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 50%; background: #D7FF01; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .lbl-sm { color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); font-size: 6.8px; }
        .val-sm { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 2px; }
        .pair-row { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-top: 8px; }
        .pair { flex: 1; }
        .addr-block { margin-top: 8px; }
        .route-wrap { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-top: 10px; gap: 12px; }
        .route-left { width: 44%; min-width: 0; }
        .timeline { padding-left: 22px; position: relative; }
        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 6px;
            top: 4px;
            bottom: 4px;
            width: 1px;
            background: #000;
        }
        .tl-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 4px; }
        .tl-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -19px;
            top: 3px;
            width: 7px;
            height: 7px;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #fff;
        }
        /* Outer frame: шире высоты тайла → object-fit: cover заполняет ширину (см. InvoiceStaticMapFetcher). */
        .map-box {
            width: 320px;
            height: 118px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 2.85px solid #000000;
            border-radius: 6px;
            position: relative;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            background: #e8e8e8;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .map-box-inner {
            position: absolute;
            left: 2.85px;
            top: 2.85px;
            width: calc(320px - 5.7px);
            height: calc(118px - 5.7px);
        }
        .map-box-inner img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: center;
            display: block;
        }
        /* Pins: круги с обводкой 2.85px как в макете (Pickup — белый, Delivery — #DEDEDE). */
        .map-pin {
            position: absolute;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            box-sizing: content-box;
            border: 2.85px solid #000000;
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            z-index: 2;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .map-pin-pickup { background: #ffffff; }
        .map-pin-drop { background: #DEDEDE; }
        .svc-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 12px; }
        .price-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-top: 8px;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
        }
        .price-cell { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
        .price-cell .lbl-sm { min-height: 22px; }
        .price-cell .val-sm { font-weight: 500; }
        .price-cell.total .val-sm { font-weight: 700; }
        .pay-grid { display: flex; gap: 48px; margin-top: 8px; }
        .legal-note { color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); font-size: 7px; max-width: 220px; margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.35; }
        .footer {
            position: absolute;
            left: 12mm;
            right: 12mm;
            bottom: 10mm;
            padding-top: 6px;
            border-top: 0.5px solid #ccc;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 6px;
            color: rgba(34,32,31,0.3);
        }
        .footer .right { text-align: right; max-width: 58%; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
    <div class="hdr-row">
        <div class="title">Rēķins</div>
        <div class="meta">
            <div class="meta-block">
                <div class="lbl">Rēķina Nr / Pasūtījuma Nr</div>
                <div class="val">{{ invoice_number }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-block">
                <div class="lbl">Rēķina datums:</div>
                <div class="val">{{ issue_date }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="logo-block">
            <div class="logo-name">hevvi</div>
            <div>Heavy stuff, delivered quickly.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="line">

    <div class="two-col">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="sec-title"><span class="dot"></span> Pakalpojuma sniedzējs</div>
            <hr class="line">
            <div class="lbl-sm">Pārdevējs (Pakalpojuma sniedzējs):</div>
            <div class="val-sm">{{ seller_name }}</div>
            <div class="pair-row">
                <div class="pair">
                    <div class="lbl-sm">Reģ. Nr.</div>
                    <div class="val-sm">{{ seller_reg }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="pair">
                    <div class="lbl-sm">PVN reģ. Nr.</div>
                    <div class="val-sm">{{ seller_vat }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="addr-block">
                <div class="lbl-sm">Juridiskā adrese:</div>
                <div class="val-sm">{{ seller_line1 }}</div>
                {% if seller_line2 %}<div class="val-sm">{{ seller_line2 }}</div>{% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="pair-row">
                <div class="pair">
                    <div class="lbl-sm">E-pasts:</div>
                    <div class="val-sm">{{ seller_email }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="pair">
                    <div class="lbl-sm">Tālrunis:</div>
                    <div class="val-sm">{{ seller_phone }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="sec-title"><span class="dot"></span> Pakalpojumu saņēmējs</div>
            <hr class="line">
            <div class="lbl-sm">Pircējs (Klients):</div>
            <div class="val-sm">{{ buyer_company }}</div>
            <div class="pair-row">
                <div class="pair">
                    <div class="lbl-sm">Reģ. Nr.</div>
                    <div class="val-sm">{{ buyer_reg }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="pair">
                    <div class="lbl-sm">PVN reģ. Nr.</div>
                    <div class="val-sm">{{ buyer_vat }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="addr-block">
                <div class="lbl-sm">Adrese:</div>
                {% for line in buyer_address_lines %}
                    <div class="val-sm">{{ line }}</div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="route-wrap">
        <div class="route-left">
            <div class="sec-title"><span class="dot"></span> Maršruts</div>
            <hr class="line">
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="tl-item">
                    <div class="lbl-sm">Pickup</div>
                    <div class="val-sm">{{ pickup }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tl-item">
                    <div class="lbl-sm">Delivery</div>
                    <div class="val-sm">{{ delivery }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="map-box">
            <div class="map-box-inner">
                <img src="{{ map_data_uri|raw }}" alt="">
                {% if map_show_pins %}
                    <span class="map-pin map-pin-pickup" style="left: {{ map_pickup_left }}px; top: {{ map_pickup_top }}px;"></span>
                    <span class="map-pin map-pin-drop" style="left: {{ map_drop_left }}px; top: {{ map_drop_top }}px;"></span>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="svc-head">
        <div class="sec-title" style="margin-top:0"><span class="dot"></span> Pakalpojums</div>
        <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:9px;">Pakalpojuma sniegšanas datums: {{ service_date }}</div>
    </div>
    <hr class="line">

    <div class="price-grid">
        <div class="price-cell">
            <div class="lbl-sm">Kravas piegādes maksa</div>
            <div class="val-sm">{{ amount_freight }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-cell">
            <div class="lbl-sm">{{ commission_label }}</div>
            <div class="val-sm">{{ amount_commission }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-cell">
            <div class="lbl-sm">Starpsumma (bez PVN)</div>
            <div class="val-sm">{{ amount_subtotal }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-cell">
            <div class="lbl-sm">{{ vat_label }}</div>
            <div class="val-sm">{{ amount_vat }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-cell total">
            <div class="lbl-sm">KOPĀ APMAKSAI (ar PVN)</div>
            <div class="val-sm">{{ amount_gross }}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:14px">
        <div class="sec-title"><span class="dot"></span> Maksājuma informācija</div>
        <hr class="line">
        <div class="pay-grid">
            <div>
                <div class="lbl-sm">Maksājuma veids</div>
                <div class="val-sm">Bankas pārskaitījums</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="lbl-sm">Apmaksas termiņš</div>
                <div class="val-sm">{{ due_date }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="legal-note">
            Rēķins sagatavots elektroniski un ir derīgs bez paraksta. PVN piemērots saskaņā ar Pievienotās vērtības nodokļa likumu.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <div><span class="logo-name" style="font-size:8px;">hevvi</span> — Pakalpojums sniegts caur Hevvi digitālo platformu</div>
        <div class="right">Hevvi App nodrošina digitālu platformu transporta pakalpojumu organizēšanai. Komisijas maksa tiek ieturēta par platformas izmantošanu un administrēšanu.</div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
